        "subject": "LU-16107 wbc: more tests about cache evicting under WBC",
        "message": "LU-16107 wbc: more tests about cache evicting under WBC\n\nThis patch adds test cases sanity-wbc/119,120 for cache evicting\nunder WBC.\nsanity-wbc/119 tests cache evicting on a subtree with de-completed\nfiles.\nsanity-wbc/120 tests cache evicting for a regular file with page\ncache committed.\n\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Id7292646de2a758c547c335135df55c5a7c9dd8d\n"
      },
